---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.jsx";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Technology Health Check"
  page="home"
  description="Technology Health Check for growing businesses: reduce costs, remove waste, lower risk, and simplify IT with clear 90-day priorities."
>
  <Navbar client:load />

  <main class="page-main">
    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10">
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base font-bold tracking-wide uppercase" style="color: var(--color-accent-purple);">
          Practical first step for growing businesses
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white mt-4">
          Technology Health Check: reduce cost, risk, waste, and complexity
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-5 text-lg md:text-xl" style="color: var(--muted);">
          The Technology Health Check gives leadership a clear view of systems, vendors, risks, and priorities. It is a focused,
          business-first way to understand what is working, what is creating drag, and what should happen next—without needing to hire
          a full-time CTO first.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-extrabold transition hover:brightness-110"
            style="background: var(--color-accent-green); color: #08110c; box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(57,255,122,0.22);"
          >
            Book a free initial consultation
          </a>
          <a
            href="/services"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold border border-white/15 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/15 transition text-white"
          >
            View all services
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-10">
      <div class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">Who it is for</h2>
        <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg list-disc list-inside" style="color: var(--muted);">
          <li>Growing businesses relying on more systems, vendors, and tools</li>
          <li>Businesses seeing technology costs rise without clear value</li>
          <li>Leadership teams making IT decisions reactively</li>
          <li>Organisations facing increasing cyber, operational, or vendor risk</li>
          <li>Teams needing clearer priorities without hiring a full-time CTO</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-5 text-base md:text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
          For a practical perspective before engaging, read <a href="/insights/signs-your-business-has-outgrown-ad-hoc-it-decisions" class="underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white text-white">Signs your business has outgrown ad hoc IT decisions</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-10">
      <div class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">What the Technology Health Check looks at</h2>
        <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg list-disc list-inside" style="color: var(--muted);">
          <li>Systems, tools, and vendor landscape</li>
          <li>Overlap, waste, and unnecessary technology spend</li>
          <li>Operational friction and process gaps</li>
          <li>Cyber and resilience risks</li>
          <li>Ownership, accountability, and decision gaps</li>
          <li>Immediate opportunities to simplify and improve</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-10">
      <div class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">What you get</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-5">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-white">Clear risk and efficiency picture</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-base md:text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
              A clear view of major risks, inefficiencies, and opportunities across systems, vendors, and delivery.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-5">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-white">Quick wins and cost savings</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-base md:text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
              Practical actions you can take early to remove waste, reduce spend, and improve day-to-day operations.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-5">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-white">Prioritised recommendations</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-base md:text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
              Ranked priorities so leadership can focus effort and budget where it will deliver the strongest outcomes.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-5">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-white">Practical 90-day plan</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-base md:text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
              A practical 90-day view of what should happen next, with clearer decision-making support for leadership.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-10 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">Why this is a good first step</h2>
        <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg list-disc list-inside" style="color: var(--muted);">
          <li>Low-friction starting point with immediate clarity</li>
          <li>Practical, business-focused recommendations</li>
          <li>Independent advice, not vendor-led upsell</li>
          <li>No unnecessary long-term dependency</li>
          <li>Can lead into deeper advisory support only where useful</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">How it fits the Aurora ICT model</h2>
        <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg list-disc list-inside" style="color: var(--muted);">
          <li>Start here when your business needs clarity</li>
          <li>Continue into planning or implementation support only if needed</li>
          <li>Stop once you have the confidence and structure to move forward</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-5 text-base md:text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
          This modular approach keeps the engagement proportionate to your business needs and priorities. See the broader
          advisory options on the <a href="/services" class="underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white text-white">Services page</a>. After the Technology Health Check, Aurora ICT can help shape the right ongoing support and leadership model through <a href="/it-support-and-fractional-cto/" class="underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white text-white">Aurora ICT Total Care</a> — covering IT planning, leadership and service in one tailored package.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          <a href="/it-support-and-fractional-cto/" class="font-bold" style="color: var(--color-accent-green);">Explore Aurora ICT Total Care →</a>
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base md:text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
          You may also find our <a href="/insights/building-a-practical-security-baseline" class="underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white text-white">security baseline guidance</a> useful when prioritising resilience improvements.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-20">
      <div class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">Ready for a clear next step?</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Book a free initial consultation to discuss your current environment and decide whether a Technology Health Check is the right place to start.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-extrabold transition hover:brightness-110"
            style="background: var(--color-accent-green); color: #08110c; box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(57,255,122,0.22);"
          >
            Book a free initial consultation
          </a>
          <a
            href="/services"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold border border-white/15 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/15 transition text-white"
          >
            Explore modular services
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
